  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江社团一档写作类社刊，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/mag/135231930/\" style=\"color: rgb(0,90,148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江社团订阅本社刊！</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://athomewithgrowingold.com/wp-content/uploads/home-slides-081.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"点击查看原图\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px;\"><img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/shetuan/c3a1a7b5-2cab-49c3-92c1-711c612e12b9.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px; height: 321px;\" />&nbsp;</span></a><span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0,0,0);\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tAim<br />\n\tAim means setting one's goal towards something. What is the aim? Who is aiming? What will be the outcome?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They aimed... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) precise aim</p>\n<p>\n\t2) aim for gold<br />\n\t3) aim for success<br />\n\t4) aim at the target<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tInstead of aiming for full workout sessions, he decided to add exercise into his daily routine. Rather than taking the elevator when going downstairs, he would almost always choose the stairs if he was traveling by himself. When going with other people, then of course he would just take the elevator ride down along with everyone else, for it would seem rude to walk away saying he would meet them downstairs. He found that changing small habits and choose to be more active was much easier for him to handle.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/1710164962111/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p912801/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p912801\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p968558/\">福利！第一时间获取四六级答案！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p965978/\">独家：2016年12月四六级翻